<C>__{ann}
<D>__{we...don't usually let people smoke in the house. we have a patio if you }
<C>__{graham}
<D>__{oh, no problem. it can wait.}
<A>__{a moment of silence. graham looks at ann directly. it is not a challenging stare, he's just trying to ascertain what kind of person she is. ann, to her credit, somehow meets his gaze. something subtle passes between them.}
<C>__{ann}
<P>__{(looks at duffle bag)}
<D>__{do you have other things?}
