<D>__{oh, you mean to bring in! no. yes, i have some other things, no, i don't need to bring them in. this is all i need to stay here.}
<C>__{ann}
<D>__{oh.}
<A>__{graham smiles. he has an unusual face, a face that fluctuates between remarkably handsome and just plain strange.}
<C>__{graham}
<D>__{have you ever been on television?}
<C>__{ann}
<D>__{televison?}
<C>__{graham}
<D>__{yes.}
<C>__{ann}
<D>__{no. why?}
